    <p class="gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Changes to copyright law after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This guidance covers the impacts on UK right holders, businesses, cultural heritage institutions and consumers. It is not legal advice.</p>

  </div>
</div>

